---
// About.astro
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">About Me</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 mx-auto mt-2 rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Left: About Text -->
      <div class="space-y-10">
        <!-- Currently Learning -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star-icon lucide-star w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300  "><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">Currently Learning</p>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed ">
            I'm constantly expanding my knowledge in modern web development, focusing on React ecosystem, backend technologies, and cloud infrastructure. Currently diving deep into Go for backend development and exploring AWS services for scalable applications.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Favorite Technologies -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star-icon lucide-star w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">Favorite Technologies</p>
          </h3>
          
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">React</span>
            <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 dark:bg-purple-900 dark:text-purple-300 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 dark:bg-green-900 dark:text-green-300 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Go</span>
            <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 dark:bg-orange-900 dark:text-orange-300 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Docker</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Future Goals -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star-icon lucide-star w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">
              Future Goals
            </p>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            My goal is to become a full-stack engineer capable of building scalable, user-friendly applications that solve real-world problems. I'm particularly interested in contributing to open-source projects and building products that make a positive impact.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Role Card -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-200 dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-700 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl mt-24 hover:scale-105 group transition-all duration-1200">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-code-icon lucide-code group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-1000 text-white"><path d="m16 18 6-6-6-6"/><path d="m8 6-6 6 6 6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-1000">Overview.</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          I’m currently studying Computer Systems in the Faculty of Information Science at Aichi Institute of Technology.
          I’m passionate about learning and constantly improving my skills — and I’m excited to grow even more as a developer!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
